00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:15,800
Sorry. The kitchen is a little busy today.

269
00:16:15,800 --> 00:16:18,500
These are our freshly baked Mahjong cookies. Please have a taste.

270
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:20,500
Thank you.

271
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:24,200
Enjoy.

272
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:25,300
Thank you.

273
00:16:26,400 --> 00:16:31,000
