274
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:34,000
♫ <i>Twilight awakens the stars</i> ♫

275
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:39,200
♫ <i>These moments sparkle with wonder</i> ♫

276
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,700
Two oranges and two pears, right?

277
00:16:42,700 --> 00:16:43,900
Yes.

